line_1: Sure 't was no earthly Gain that charm'd you to't,
line_2: Nothing but hopes of Heaven should make me do't:

line_1: 'Till crook or cur had set 'em to't.
line_2: How they'd not stir a single foot,

line_1: But goes with divers fears and pains to't,
line_2: Although she's hid behind the wainscot.
